--------------------><-------------------------><---------------------

<|> 𝐕𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞𝐬 -->  It is a container that store value in a Java program.
                  In another word ,, Variables are place holder for storing data.

                     Example --> int value = 10 
                             ( 'Value' is a variable and hold data '10'.)

-------------------><--------------------------><-----------------------

<|> 𝐕𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 <|>

       >> 𝑽𝒂𝒓𝒊𝒂𝒃𝒍𝒆𝒔 𝑵𝒂𝒎𝒆 --> A label for memory location.

       >> 𝑽𝒂𝒍𝒖𝒆 --> The value or data that would stored in variables.

       >> 𝑺𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒂𝒈𝒆 --> A place where data can be stored.

       >> 𝑫𝒆𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏 --> Announce a variable usually when begins your program. (When you explain variable).

--------------------------><---------------------------------><----------------------------

<|> 𝐍𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐟 𝐕𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞𝐬 <|>
       A set of rules for naming a Java variables.

          >> A variable name must start with a letter , underscore character.
          >> A variable cannot start with a number.
          >> A variable name can only contain alpha-numeric characters and underscore ( 0-9 , A - z and _ ).
          >> Variable name are case sensitive ( Age , age , AGE - Different three variable).

            -- Example of Variables --

        <> 𝑽𝒂𝒍𝒊𝒅 𝑽𝒂𝒓𝒊𝒂𝒃𝒍𝒆𝒔 𝑵𝒂𝒎𝒆𝒔 ---> 

               :: int Valid_num = 10   / Valid_Num = 10
               :: int valid_num = 20   / valid_Num = 20
               :: int _Validnum = 30
               :: int Validnum1 = 40
               :: int validnum2 = 50
               :: int valid = 10    /  Valid = 10

         <> I𝒏𝒗𝒂𝒍𝒊𝒅 𝑽𝒂𝒓𝒊𝒂𝒃𝒍𝒆𝒔 𝑵𝒂𝒎𝒆𝒔 ---> 
           
               :: int 1Valid_num = 10 
               :: int 2validnum = 20 
               :: int 3_Validnum = 30

 Note-->> I use int here, Same variable name with all data type, like string, float, long, etc.

--------------------------><---------------------------------><----------------------------

|><| 𝐕𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐢𝐧 𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐜𝐨𝐝𝐞 -->>

class Variable
{
    public static void main (String []args )
    {
        int number = 5;        //
        int number_2 = 10;    //
        int Number = 15;     //   These are valid variable
        int NUM = 20;       //

        String Person_name = "Java";     //
        String person_name = "java";     //  These are valid variable
        String _person = "java";         //

  //      int 2num = 10;         //
  //      Number = 15;           //   These are not valid variable
 //       int 1_person = 20;     //

    }
}


